      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) measured in bench tests is the direct experimental analog to the relative hemolysis index (RH) used in the COU acceptance criterion. Velocity field validation provides additional confidence in the flow physics underpinning the hemolysis power-law model."
