      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, operating conditions, and fluid properties sufficiently representative of COU device and use conditions.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump — the same geometry used in the COU. Operating points bracket the clinical CPB range (2–5 L/min, 3000–3500 RPM). Bovine blood used in bench tests; species correction factor applied per published literature. Validation scenario rated as representative of COU."
    },
